name: $JOBIDnode$JOBMULT-realign
script: mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/mount -t nfs singlefs1-fileserver:/testzfs /mnt/zfs/mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/MakeIntervalList.py|./' --F './MakeIntervalList.py'python ./MakeIntervalList.py --F interval.interval_list --C '$JOBMULTNODASH'java -Xmx2g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs/$JOBID/ -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T RealignerTargetCreator -R /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /mnt/zfs/cancer.sorted.dedup.bam -I /mnt/zfs/normal.sorted.dedup.bam -known /mnt/zfs/1000G_phase1.indels.b37.vcf -known /mnt/zfs/Mills_and_1000G_gold_standard.indels.b37.vcf -o /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/GATKRealignTargets.intervals -nt 4 -L interval.interval_listrm /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/GATKRealignTargets.intervalsjava -Xmx2g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs/$JOBID/ -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T RealignerTargetCreator -R
